 RAP star and fashionista Riky Rick is becoming a year older tomorrow and the only thing he wants is to put someone with talent on blast – and it could be you. If you are a singer, songwriter or a creative then Ricky wants you to help him finish off his lyrics of his brand-new single Rain On Me. For a birthday gift, the star wants to give someone a chance to shine and become a star just like him. Taking to his social media, he said he wants to hit the studio next week but needs help with finishing off lyrics to his new song Rain On me. He tweeted: “My birthday is officially 2mow the only thing I want as a gift is for somebody, a singer/songwriter, a creative to finish off these lyrics for me. Director come with a concept for visuals. Let’s collaborate. Tag a friend. We go to studio next week”.  